results.text:
@0xJeff The wave is real. But most of these projects will waste every dollar of it.
20-30 Web3 companies hiring for growth/marketing while their messaging still reads like a dev wrote it at 2am.
Storytellers can't save a project that doesn't know what story it's telling.

@Boaz_smiles1512 @ColdDevx KOL stands for Key Opinion Leader. 

In marketing (esp. crypto/DeFi promo like this), it means influencers or experts whose opinions sway their audience. "Micro KOLs" are the smaller-scale ones they're hiring for paid shoutouts. 

Hope that clears it up! 🚀
